{{Wireless embedded system |brand=Westell |model=Versalink |revision=7550 (B90-755025-15) |price=100 |fcc_date=04/01/2011 |manuf_country=China |is_manuf=No |manuf=Askey |manuf_model=RTA4515W-D27 |availability=common |type=wireless router,dsl modem |fcc_id=CH8B755 |us_id=5KPDL01B755 |pwr_v=12 |pwr_amp=1 |pwr_conn=barrel |cpu1_brand=Lantiq |cpu1_model=PSB 50810;XWAY ARX168 (PSB 50810 EL V1.2); |cpu1_cspeed=333 |fla1=8 |fla1_brand=Spansion |fla1_model=S29GL064N90TFI04 |ram1=32 |ram1_brand=Winbond |ram1_model=W9425G6JH-5 |serial=yes,, 4-pin header,, populated,, 3.3V TTL,, (115200,8,N,1),, J1 |wi1_chip1_brand=Atheros |wi1_chip1_model=AR9227 |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_txchains=2 |wi1_rxchains=2 |wi1_sstreams=2 |eth_cpu=true |sw_brand=Lantiq |sw_model=PSB 6970;XWAY TANTOS (PSB 6970 V V1.3); |lan_speed=100M |lan_ports=4 |flags=ADSL2+ |stock_boot=Westell ROM Bootloader;1.1.3;; |stock_os=Linux;2.6.20.19;; |802dot11_protocols=bgn |default_ssid=ATTXXXX |default_ssid_regex=^ATT[0-9]{4}$ |default_ip=192.168.1.254 |oui=74:44:01 |oui_eth=74:44:01 }} This device is a '''Westell 7550 (Netgear)'''. :It was used with '''AT&T''''s DSL service.
"RTA4515W-D27(RoHS)" is silkscreened on the board. :FCC photos show a USB port, but on hand example does not have it populated.
Per [http://screenshots.portforward.com/routers/Netgear/B90-755025-15/Log.htm this router UI screenshot], this device uses an '''Atheros''' wireless chip. :CPU: [[Lantiq]] XWAY ARX168 (PSB 50810 EL V1.2) @333MHz :Switch: [[Lantiq]] XWAY TANTOS (PSB 6970 V V1.3)
